column10:
[h1]There is no cure for this madness[/h1]

[b]Day 01[/b] - Returning home to quench my thirst for righteousness, arriving with curiosity and hopefulness, I claim my birthright and seek to fulfill my ancestors duties; 

[b]Day 05[/b] - Old letters, words that pierce my mind and make me doubt my true motives, there is no going back, the old road pulls me away;

[b]Day 08[/b] - Curiosity arrives, a band of brave or mad in seek to find loot or truth, we march towards the catacombs and silence is our song; 

[b]Day 12[/b] - Our path is not the same or maybe we are the strangers, arriving town brings comfort but despair is in our eyes;

[b]Day 19[/b] - There is a shadow lurking around, my past and future in front of me. Am I to fail as my ancestor did or to bring justice to out family;

[b]Day 22[/b] - Bravest of heroes are afflicted by curses of their own mind, there is no escape;

[b]Day 71[/b] - No hope left, we advance to The Darkest Dungeon; 

[b]Day 71[/b] - This is no game, but the downfall of my family;

[b][....] [/b] Follow the old road, come to the mansion and make it your own, end what we started and let madness free your mind.
